div.p:
Yea amongst Real Christians, one must strive to Excel another; A good strife this is (— 
                     〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
                  ) to provoke to Love and good works, not onely by words but deeds; to strive who shall do most for God, who shall most Abound in His Work, Labour most in his Vineyard, who shall live Best. But then they that Abound and Excel others, must also Excel in Humility; So S. Paul in 2 Cor. 12. 11. and 1 Cor. 15. 10.
